Definations to be used for new backlog items
•	clear and short title
•	what value does it bring (e.g. critical fix, improve user experience)?
•	describes the problem sufficiently
•	is the implementation of the ticket clear or does it need to be clarified?
•	add a clothing size
•	add related labels (ready for dev label) or other related item numbers
•	milestone are filled in refinements
